<p style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: '冬青黑体简体中文 W3', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 29px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;">怡元康营销管理（河北）有限公司，<span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit;">主打产品为</span>开心果牛奶和烧酸奶。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: '冬青黑体简体中文 W3', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 29px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;">开心果牛奶采用新西兰有机奶源与俄罗斯开心果精心制作，运用了高温瞬间碳化工艺，原汁原味地保留着牛奶的浓郁与开心果的清香。</span></p>
<p style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: '冬青黑体简体中文 W3', 微软雅黑, 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-indent: 29px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑;">烧酸奶，颠覆传统酸奶制作工艺，与普通酸奶是将鲜牛奶先经过杀菌后添加益生菌发酵方式不同的是，烧酸奶是将牛奶先经过数个小时的低温加热，然后再添加益生菌发酵而成，这样的制作工艺让酸奶从颜色、状态、口感上都保证为天然形成。</span></p>
